sense.gloss: to overlook, to fail to notice, to miss (seeing)

sdata.j: その↑家↑↓いえ↓は↑教会↑↓きょうかい↓の↑向↑↓む↓かいだから↑見落↑↓|みお↓とす|はずはない。
sdata.e: The house is opposite the church. You can't miss it.

sdata.j: その↑家↑↓いえ↓は↑教会↑↓きょうかい↓の↑向↑↓む↓かいだから↑見落↑↓|みお↓とす|はずはない。
sdata.e: The house is across from the church, so you shouldn't miss it.
